                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Cancel interest in a session (authenticated).</p>
                 <p><strong>Parameters:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                     <li><code>sessionId</code>: The ID of the session.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint-block">
                <h4>GET /api/post/user</h4>
                <p><strong>Method:</strong> GET</p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Retrieve user's interested sessions (authenticated).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint-block">
                <h4>GET /api/post/:sessionId/all</h4>
                <p><strong>Method:</strong> GET</p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Retrieve all interests for a session (authenticated).</p>
                 <p><strong>Parameters:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                     <li><code>sessionId</code>: The ID of the session.</li>
