            </div>
            <div class="endpoint-block">
                <h4>GET /api/post/notifications</h4>
                <p><strong>Method:</strong> GET</p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Get notifications related to interests (authenticated).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint-block">
                <h4>PUT /api/post/notifications/read</h4>
                <p><strong>Method:</strong> PUT</p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Mark notifications as read (authenticated).</p>
